subject: Tennis
French Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Kristina Mladenovic of France beat Li Na on Tuesday, 7-5, 3-6, 6-1, which means the Australian Open’s two singles winners, Li and Stan Wawrinka, have both been eliminated.
